    <h1 class="jumbotron-heading">About CrimeRate</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted" style="font-size: 0.8em">
      At CrimeRate, we all come to work every day because we want to solve the biggest problem in crime.
        <strong>Everyone is guessing.</strong> Working people don't know who can help them to finally kill their bosses,
        what way is the most exciting, or even what to price them at. Credulus vendors don't know where their target
        customers are, how to reach them, or even how much time they need to spend in order to do so.
        <br>
        <br>
      Throughout the history of crime, people use their own contacts, some of them even don't have one. Our mission
      at CrimeRate to make the contacts with the crime world more accessable to people who are seeking for help. Today
